Even 1-1.5 sec casting spells aren't really viable.  Anything we get needs to be in clicky form, either from AA or from an item.  Waiting for spell gems to refresh is just too long to reliably survive when the odds of getting maxhit four times in a row just aren't that terribly low.  This is the kind of thing our numerous crappy aa skills SHOULD have done but were all both too weak and FAR too long to reset.  We have stasis, doppleganger, mind over matter, soothing words, and color shock all with very long reset timers.  Compare to fading memories which now with decent gear has a 3 min 45 sec reset timer and the ability to develop a 'pool' to use it more than once in rapid succession.<br />_________________<br />-<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=648415" target="_blank" class="postlink">Londo Mollari</a> (retired)
